description: Fresh beef and chicken muscle meat combined with raw meaty bones, liver, hearts, gizzard, whole salmon and trout, green lipped mussels, salmon & olive oil, apple cider vinegar, kelp, alfalfa. Promotes healthy body condition, digestion, skin & coat, bones & joints, weight management, sensitive stomach support, probiotics & enzymes, heart/kidney/liver health, immune support, healthy teeth and gums, and proper stool volume. Feeding guideline: 2.5% of ideal weight for maintenance; 3.5–5% for active, pregnant or growing pets.

Fresh beef muscle meat and green tripe combined with whole salmon and trout. Provides high-quality protein, vitamins and minerals; supports body condition, digestion, skin & coat, bones & joints and immune system. Feeding guideline: 2.5% of ideal weight for maintenance; 3.5–5% for active, pregnant or growing pets.

Whole rabbit meat in small bites; rich source of lean protein, low in cholesterol and sodium, excellent source of vitamin B complex. Supports healthy heart, muscle development, and immune system. Particularly suitable for pets with food allergies or sensitivities. Feeding guideline: 2.5% of adult ideal weight for maintenance; up to 5% for active, pregnant or growing pets.

Whole duck meat in convenient small bites. Excellent source of protein and iron; rich in zinc, selenium and B‑complex vitamins; high in omega‑3 fatty acids for skin and coat health. Suitable for pets with food sensitivities and helps boost immune system. Feeding guideline: 2.5% of ideal weight for maintenance; 3.5–5% for active, pregnant or growing pets.

Whole turkey meat; high‑quality protein source that’s easy to digest. Rich in vitamin B‑complex, zinc and phosphorus to support brain function, immune health and strong bones. Ideal for pets with food allergies. Feeding guideline: 2.5% of ideal weight for maintenance; 3.5–5% for active or pregnant pets.

Blend of fresh fatty beef and lamb meat without bones. Provides high‑quality protein and fat to support healthy body condition, digestion, skin and coat, heart and kidney health, and sensitive stomachs. Highly nutritious and helps dogs and cats grow strong. Feeding guideline: 2.5% of ideal weight for maintenance; 3.5–5% for active, pregnant or growing pets.

Whole chicken pieces providing high protein for lean muscle mass. Balanced for both dogs and cats; rich in vitamins and minerals, tryptophan and taurine. Supports strong muscles, immune system and overall vitality. Feeding guideline: 2.5% of ideal weight for maintenance; 3.5–5% for active or pregnant pets.

Whole fresh salmon pieces providing high-quality protein, omega‑3 fatty acids and minerals. Supports bone and joint health, heart function, skin and coat health, and immune system. Suitable for pets with allergies. Feeding guideline: 2.5% of ideal weight for maintenance; increase for active or growing pets.

Dehydrated beef heart chips made from all‑natural, human‑grade, single‑ingredient beef heart. Rich in protein, essential amino acids, vitamins and minerals including taurine, B vitamins and iron. Supports cardiovascular health, muscle function and overall vitality. A nutrient‑dense treat perfect for training rewards, healthy snacks or mixing into meals; aligns with raw feeding philosophy.

Dehydrated beef liver chips that are nutrient‑dense and easy to digest. High in protein, B vitamins, iron and other minerals; supports digestion, immune function, joint health and shiny coat. Ideal as high‑value training treats or healthy snacks; can be crumbled onto meals. Made from human‑grade, single ingredient beef liver.

Bulk pack of dehydrated beef liver chips with the same nutrient‑dense profile as the smaller pack. Rich in protein, vitamins and minerals; supports digestive health, immune function, joint health and shiny coat. Ideal for owners who need a larger quantity for training or regular supplementation. Use as high‑value training treats or crumble onto food.

Dehydrated chicken hearts that provide a rich source of protein and essential nutrients. Supports muscle development and overall well‑being; offers a palatable treat that aligns with raw feeding philosophy. Ideal as a training reward, healthy snack or to mix with food.

Dehydrated beef lung packed with protein, B‑vitamins and iron. Supports cell health, energy levels and muscle function. A crunchy single‑ingredient treat ideal for training rewards or daily snacks; can be crumbled onto meals.

Gently dried whole sardines rich in protein, omega‑3 fatty acids, calcium and vitamin D. Supports heart health, joint function, brain development and a shiny coat. Ideal as a training reward, nutritious snack or meal topper; aligns with raw feeding philosophy.

Dehydrated beef muscle meat providing lean protein, amino acids, B‑vitamins and iron. Supports muscle development, energy and overall health. Use as a high‑value training treat, healthy snack or crumble onto meals. Made from human‑grade single ingredient.

Larger pack of dehydrated beef muscle meat offering lean protein, essential amino acids, B‑vitamins and iron. Supports muscle growth, energy and overall well‑being. Perfect for training or daily snacking; can be crumbled onto meals; made from single ingredient beef.

Dehydrated beef heart chips rich in protein, taurine, B‑vitamins and iron. Supports heart function, muscle health and overall vitality. Perfect for training, snacking or mixing into meals. Single‑ingredient, human grade and aligns with raw feeding philosophy.

Dehydrated shrimp rich in protein, omega‑3 fatty acids, iodine and phosphorus. Supports healthy skin and coat, joint function and immune system. Ideal as a training reward, crunchy snack or meal topper for dogs and cats.

Gently dried beef spleen providing concentrated vitamins and minerals such as iron, vitamin A and B‑vitamins. Supports immune function, red blood cell production and overall vitality. Use as high‑value training treat or mix into meals.

Larger pack of dehydrated beef spleen offering nutrient‑dense organ meat with high levels of iron and vitamin A. Supports immune function and energy production. Ideal for training rewards, snacks or meal toppers.

Dehydrated beef liver chips in a mid‑sized pack. Rich in protein, vitamins and minerals; supports digestive health, immune function and joint health. Use as training treats or healthy snacks; can be crumbled onto meals.
Small pack of dehydrated beef lung rich in protein and iron. Ideal for small dogs or occasional treats; supports energy and muscle function.
Dehydrated chicken liver treats providing high levels of vitamin A, iron and B‑vitamins. Supports immune system, vision, and healthy skin. Use as training treats or meal toppers.
Dehydrated chicken breast strips offering lean protein and essential amino acids. Supports muscle development and energy. Ideal for training rewards or a healthy snack.

Mid‑sized pack of dehydrated chicken liver chips, rich in vitamins A, B‑vitamins and iron. Supports immune function, energy and healthy skin and coat. Great as high‑value training treats or meal toppers.
Larger pack of dehydrated chicken breast providing lean protein and essential amino acids. Supports muscle growth and overall well‑being; use as training rewards or crumble onto meals.

Natural trachea chew rich in glucosamine and chondroitin for joint support. Promotes dental health by cleaning teeth and gums while satisfying the dog’s chewing instinct. Provides mental stimulation and helps reduce destructive behaviour; ideal as a jackpot reward or healthy snack.

Dried rabbit ears with hair provide fibre for natural deworming. Rich in glucosamine and chondroitin to support joints; promote dental hygiene; release feel‑good chemicals like dopamine and serotonin for mental stimulation; reduce destructive behaviour. Ideal as a healthy snack or jackpot treat.

Natural bully sticks made from beef muscle. Promote dental health by reducing plaque and tartar; easy to digest; rich in protein and amino acids; provide mental stimulation and help reduce boredom; free from additives; satisfy chewing instinct.

Large natural trachea chew packed with glucosamine and chondroitin to support joint health. Encourages dental hygiene, satisfies the natural urge to chew, promotes mental and physical stimulation, and reduces destructive behaviour. Perfect as a jackpot reward or healthy snack.

Dried back strap chews rich in glucosamine and chondroitin. Support joint health, promote dental hygiene and provide mental stimulation. Ideal for chewing sessions that reduce boredom and destructive behaviour.

Set of five small bully sticks that offer dental benefits, are easy to digest and packed with protein and amino acids. Provide mental stimulation, natural and safe chewing and last long enough to keep dogs occupied.

Braided bully stick crafted from natural beef muscle. Supports dental health, is highly digestible, offers substantial chewing time and provides protein and amino acids for overall health. Natural and free from additives.

Twisted bully stick that reduces plaque and tartar, is easy to digest and rich in protein. Provides mental stimulation, natural chewing satisfaction and long‑lasting enjoyment; free from additives and preservatives.

Natural beef tendons rich in glucosamine and chondroitin to support joint health. Promote dental hygiene by scraping teeth and gums, provide mental stimulation and reduce destructive behaviour. Ideal as a jackpot treat or healthy chew.

Beef ear with hair acting as natural dewormer by increasing fibre and sweeping away undigested food. Rich in glucosamine and chondroitin for joints; promotes dental hygiene and satisfies chewing instinct; releases dopamine and serotonin for mental stimulation; reduces destructive behaviour.

Dehydrated beef tripe providing natural prebiotics and enzymes for digestive health. Also offers dental benefits, mental stimulation and behavioural improvement. A single‑ingredient chew that supports gut health and aligns with raw feeding philosophy.

Spiral‑shaped bully stick made from natural beef muscle. Supports dental health, is easy to digest, provides protein and amino acids, offers mental stimulation, and satisfies chewing instincts. Long‑lasting and free from additives.

Dehydrated chicken feet rich in glucosamine and chondroitin to support joint health. Promote dental hygiene by scraping teeth and gums; provide mental stimulation and behavioural benefits. Ideal after training or as a healthy chew.

Premium dehydrated shark chew, rich in protein and omega‑3 fatty acids. Sustainably sourced and free of additives, it provides a long‑lasting chewing experience and nutrients for healthy skin, coat and joints. Suitable for pets with dietary sensitivities needing a protein boost.

Braided salmon skin chews rich in omega‑3 fatty acids. Support healthy skin, coat and joints; supply high‑quality protein for muscle maintenance; promote cardiovascular health and boost immunity; cleaning teeth while dogs chew.

Small duck necks dehydrated to provide natural calcium, phosphorus, glucosamine and chondroitin. Support bone and joint health while satisfying chewing instincts. Ideal for puppies and small dogs; helps clean teeth and gums.

Large duck neck chews gently dehydrated to retain nutrients. Offer high levels of calcium, phosphorus, glucosamine and chondroitin; support bones, joints and dental health; provide mental stimulation for dogs.

Blend of blueberry, raspberry and cranberry powders rich in antioxidants, vitamins and fibre. Supports immune system, urinary tract health, reduces inflammation, promotes healthy skin and coat and overall vitality. Each berry provides specific benefits: blueberries support brain health, raspberries aid digestion and cranberries promote urinary tract health.

Organic spirulina powder packed with proteins, vitamins (A, B‑complex, C, D, E, K), minerals (iron, calcium, magnesium, potassium, zinc, copper, manganese, sodium, selenium), antioxidants (phycocyanin, beta‑carotene) and essential fatty acids (omega‑3 & 6). Supports immune system, boosts energy, improves skin and coat, aids digestion and reduces inflammation.

Pumpkin powder supplement for digestive health. Rich in fibre to support digestion and bowel regularity; helps maintain healthy weight by providing satiety; contains vitamins A, C and E; antioxidants boost immune system; soothes stomach discomfort. Easy to sprinkle over food.

Granulated beef topper that enhances flavour and provides additional protein and nutrients. Helps encourage picky eaters, adds variety to meals, supports muscle maintenance and weight management. Coarser texture adds crunch and interest to meals.

Beef bone broth rich in collagen, glucosamine and amino acids. Supports joint health, digestive health and hydration; provides minerals and boosts palatability. Useful for recovery after illness or to entice fussy eaters.

Powdered fish topper to enhance flavour and nutrition. Provides high‑quality protein, omega‑3 fatty acids and essential nutrients; encourages picky eaters; supports muscle maintenance, weight management and variety. Powder blends easily into food.
Finely ground beef powder topper that mixes evenly into food to boost flavour and protein. Encourages picky eaters and adds nutrients to meals; supports muscle maintenance and variety.
Granulated fish topper providing a coarser texture and a concentrated source of protein and omega‑3 fatty acids. Adds crunch and variety; encourages picky eaters and supports healthy skin and coat.

All‑natural, human‑grade single ingredient beef fillets. Selected from grass‑fed beef liver cuts; nutrient‑dense and palatable. Supports digestion, immune function, joint health and shiny coat. Research shows grass‑fed beef contains higher levels of nutrients, phytonutrients and antioxidants than grain‑fed beef.

Free‑range chicken breast fillets; all‑natural, human‑grade single ingredient. Nutrient‑dense and palatable; supports overall health including digestion, immune function, joints and coat. Free‑range chickens have healthier meat with less stress hormones and better muscle development.

Free‑range duck breast fillets; all‑natural, human‑grade and single ingredient. Support digestion, immune function, joint health and coat condition. Duck meat is rich in protein, vitamins and minerals; contains omega‑3 and omega‑6 fatty acids; novel protein suitable for pets with sensitivities.

Training treats combining robust flavours of buffalo and beef. Rich in protein and essential nutrients to support pets’ health; small size is easy to handle during training; helps reinforce good behaviour and keeps pets motivated.
Training treats combining chicken and fish flavours. High in protein and nutrients; small and easy to handle; motivate pets during training sessions and provide a healthy reward.
Bulk pack of buffalo and beef training nibbles offering robust flavour and high protein. Small pieces perfect for reinforcing good behaviour; ideal for training sessions or high‑volume reward use.
Larger pack of chicken and fish nibbles with the same high protein and rich flavour profile as the smaller size. Ideal for extended training sessions or owners needing more treats.

Freeze‑dried duck breast made from 100% duck. Rich in high‑quality protein, vitamins and minerals; freeze‑drying preserves flavour and nutrients. Perfect as a training reward, healthy snack or meal topper.
Freeze‑dried beef cubes made from 100% beef. Provide lean protein and essential nutrients; freeze‑drying locks in flavour; ideal as high‑value training reward or snack; can be mixed into meals.

Freeze‑dried quail egg yolk rich in essential fatty acids, vitamins and minerals. Supports healthy skin, coat and immune system; gentle on sensitive stomachs. Suitable as training reward, snack or meal topper.

Freeze‑dried chicken egg yolks packed with essential fatty acids and vitamins A, D, E and B‑complex. Support immune system, skin and coat health, bone health and energy levels; freeze‑drying preserves nutrients; ideal for pets of all sizes as training reward or meal topper.

Freeze‑dried New Zealand green lipped mussels rich in omega‑3 fatty acids, vitamins and minerals. Support joint health, skin and coat condition and overall vitality. Serve as training reward, special treat or crumble onto meals.

Freeze‑dried chicken breast providing lean protein, B‑vitamins and selenium. Supports muscle growth and immune health; freeze‑drying preserves nutrients; hypoallergenic and free from grains; suitable for pets with sensitive stomachs.

Freeze‑dried Antarctic krill packed with omega‑3 fatty acids, antioxidants and essential nutrients. Supports heart health, skin and coat condition and vitality. Serve as training reward, healthy snack or meal topper.

Freeze‑dried chicken cubes made from premium chicken breast; rich in lean protein, vitamins and minerals. Freeze‑drying preserves flavour; hypoallergenic; ideal for training rewards, snacks or meal toppers.
Freeze‑dried duck cubes made from 100% duck breast; rich in protein and essential nutrients. Freeze‑drying maintains flavour; perfect as training reward or special treat for dogs and cats.
Freeze‑dried chicken liver cubes packed with vitamins (A, iron, B‑vitamins) and minerals. Support immune system, skin and coat and overall vitality. Use as training reward, snack or meal topper.

Freeze‑dried Atlantic salmon providing high‑quality protein and omega‑3 fatty acids. Supports heart health, joint function, skin and coat; freeze‑drying preserves nutrients; ideal as training reward or meal topper.

Freeze‑dried duck liver rich in vitamin A, iron and essential fatty acids. Supports immune function and healthy skin and coat. Great for pets with food sensitivities; use as training treat or meal topper.
Freeze‑dried chunks of salmon skin rich in omega‑3 fatty acids. Support healthy skin and coat, joint health and cardiovascular health while providing a crunchy texture pets love.
Freeze‑dried tuna pieces offering high protein and omega‑3 fatty acids. Support heart health, brain development, skin and coat condition; perfect as training treat or meal topper.

Freeze‑dried capelin fish providing whole prey nutrition with protein, omega‑3 fatty acids and calcium. Supports dental hygiene, joint health and overall vitality; great as chewy snack or meal supplement.
Freeze‑dried salmon cubes rich in high‑quality protein and omega‑3 fatty acids. Support muscle maintenance, skin and coat health and overall vitality; serve as training treats or meal toppers.

Blend of freeze‑dried seafood pieces (assortment of fish and shellfish) providing a variety of proteins, omega‑3 fatty acids and minerals. Supports joint health, skin and coat and immune system; excellent as a special reward or topper.
Large bag of freeze‑dried beef chunks delivering concentrated protein and nutrients. Suitable for meal toppers or larger dogs that require bigger bites; freeze‑drying preserves flavour and nutrition.

Assortment of freeze‑dried fish chunks offering high‑quality protein and omega‑3 fatty acids. Provides variety and supports healthy skin, coat, joints and heart. Ideal as meal topper or treat for larger dogs.

Powdered goat milk supplement providing easily digestible proteins, calcium and vitamins. Supports digestion, hydration and healthy growth; ideal for puppies, kittens or pets needing gentle nourishment.
Salmon oil supplement rich in omega‑3 fatty acids (EPA & DHA). Supports healthy skin and coat, joint flexibility and cardiovascular health. Easy to pour over food.
Chewable probiotic supplement formulated to promote gut health and balanced digestion. Contains beneficial bacteria and fibre to support nutrient absorption and immune function.
Joint support formula containing glucosamine, chondroitin, MSM and omega‑3 fatty acids. Helps maintain healthy joints, cartilage and mobility; ideal for aging or active pets.
Immune‑boosting supplement with turmeric, curcumin and antioxidants. Helps reduce inflammation, supports immune system and promotes overall wellness.
Eggshell calcium supplement providing bioavailable calcium and trace minerals. Supports strong bones, teeth and muscle function. Ideal for pets on raw diets needing additional calcium.

High‑calorie supplement designed to help underweight pets gain healthy weight. Provides concentrated protein and fats, vitamins and minerals to support muscle growth and energy. Useful for recovering or picky eaters.
Large pack of weight gainer formula delivering extra calories from proteins and fats to promote healthy weight gain. Suitable for larger dogs or longer use.
Muscle‑building supplement formulated with high‑quality proteins, creatine and essential amino acids. Supports lean muscle development and recovery in working or athletic dogs.
Energy‑boosting supplement providing a blend of proteins, fats and carbohydrates plus vitamins and minerals. Designed to support high‑performance pets or those needing additional calories.
Supplement formulated to support pets with allergies. Contains a blend of natural ingredients like fish oil, probiotics and antioxidants to reduce inflammation and improve skin and coat health.
Supplement designed to enhance natural coat pigmentation using ingredients like seaweed, spirulina and vitamins. Supports vibrant colouring and healthy skin.
Blend of medicinal mushrooms such as reishi, shiitake and maitake. Supports immune health, energy, and overall vitality. Rich in beta‑glucans and antioxidants.

High‑fat supplement combining duck, lamb and beef fat. Provides a concentrated source of calories for underweight or high‑energy pets; supplies essential fatty acids to support skin, coat and energy levels.
Small pack of dehydrated beef lung rich in protein and iron. Provides crunchy, low‑fat treat ideal for small dogs or training rewards; supports energy and muscle health.
Large pack of dehydrated chicken liver providing abundant vitamin A, iron and B‑vitamins. Supports immune health, vision and skin condition; excellent as training treat or meal topper.
Dehydrated chicken hearts in a small pack. Rich in protein and essential nutrients; supports muscle development; ideal for training or occasional snacks.

Bulk pack of dehydrated beef heart chips offering high protein, taurine, B‑vitamins and iron. Supports heart and muscle health; perfect for owners requiring larger quantities for regular training or feeding.
